        "content": "<p>Hello (sorry for the title, I was not really inspired)<br>\nI am facing am issue when using <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=tsum_eq_zero_iff#doc\">docs#tsum_eq_zero_iff</a>. Here a MWE:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mathlib</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">variable</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">α</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">TopologicalSpace</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">CanonicallyOrderedCommMonoid</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">OrderClosedTopology</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">AddCommMonoid</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">example</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ℕ</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">α</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hs</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Summable</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">∑'</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"bp\">↔</span> <span class=\"bp\">∀</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">i</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"n\">tsum_eq_zero_iff</span> <span class=\"n\">hs</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>For some reason,  <code>isDefEq</code> times out while I believe that I instanciated each needed typeclasses for α. If you replace α by ℕ in the example, it works. If you replace it by ℝ, it does not.<br>\nDo you have any idea why?</p>",
        "id": 436912050,
        "sender_full_name": "Gaëtan Serré",
        "timestamp": 1714751499
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You have two <code>[TopologicalSpace α]</code> instances.</p>",
        "id": 436912342,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1714751617
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And you should have <code>CanonicallyOrdered*Add*CommMonoid</code></p>",
        "id": 436912497,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1714751660
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And then get rid of the extra <code>AddCommMonoid</code> instance.</p>",
        "id": 436912526,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1714751676
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>And this shouldn't work for <code>ℝ</code> because it's not canonically ordered (but <code>ℕ</code> is).</p>",
        "id": 436912573,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1714751704
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It would work for <code>ℝ≥0</code> though.</p>",
        "id": 436912609,
        "sender_full_name": "Jireh Loreaux",
        "timestamp": 1714751715
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ok thank you a lot!</p>",
